    "long_instructions": "## Try Your Own\r\n\r\nPractice asking AI about the same topic in different ways.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Reflect on these two questions.\r\n\t* How does the way we phrase a prompt influence AI contradictions?\r\n    * Why does AI provide inconsistent responses even when asked about the same topic?\r\n2. Now **try out your own example of a question**. Choose a topic, and frame your question in as many ways as possible to see if you can produce contradictions in the AI responses.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n:::details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere are some topics to consider:\r\n- Mandatory physical education in school\r\n- Free higher education\r\n- Use of AI in school assignments\r\n- The current US voting age\r\n:::",
